➜维港泊人（香港）：酒歌（三首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/417903232_100115135	17380
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>酒歌（三首）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/维港泊人（香港）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200912/fd9f216ee7674f6c93e58a023e2b2714.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《红酒》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">干杯的那刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是最浪漫的时光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都说是我品尝了你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原来是你吻醉了我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">呵，红唇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我中了你温柔的一刀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200912/5acd2e15cb0640bba3391ca96b776d4b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《白酒》</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
