➜广西诗人陈熠明：月影兰园依旧在
http://www.sohu.com/a/417909004_100115135	19620
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200912/82ff6b53b4684462ae7137b4a94ecb5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>月影兰园依旧在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•花飞梦幻笑兰亭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柔风淡淡萦烟柳，月影凭栏落水清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正是芳菲逢陌上，花飞梦幻笑兰亭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•院上兰斛嫣影在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春华梦里问青山，岁月何时送我还。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">院上兰斛嫣影在，重回往事倚栏干。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•寒窗对月过愁风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乱影花飞落锦城，寒窗对月过愁风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春华向上多磨炼，梦幻诗缘会有逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200912/31b22669506c422389b513d63bdb03df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（四）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•何愁远梦不成真</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春风静叹雨时分，燕子归来正等人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">院上兰亭花已笑，何愁远梦不成真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（五）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•诗书有梦留尘愿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧柳江边玉水逢，兰心院上赏花风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗书有梦留尘愿，四海鸿儒墨有朋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（六）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•江湖墨幻亦天娇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情缘柳岸话相邀，敢向清风问水遥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笔上兰舟花影去，江湖墨幻亦天娇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200912/067dc19fb4c24646908d804a7ca90b02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（七）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•烟随玉树已芳菲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别离远上醉青杯，古院青兰伴雪梅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月回眸多往事，烟随玉树已芳菲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（八）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•等远轮回山水恋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹阳碧树幻烟中，墨海云霞正紫红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等远轮回山水恋，相隔已是梦时空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•等你花菲梦里摘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流风错乱我情怀，等你花菲梦里摘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望水凭栏思远月，丹娇影魅正嫣开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200912/f4b83cb3d40e4b9c87b2ec1dd499b93f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·当年有我少年郎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痴心往事成沧海，暗恋姑娘梦远方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墨苑花开风雨笑，当年有我少年郎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·月影兰园依旧在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹林墨苑前缘等，笑看烟霞梦水长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月影兰园依旧在，云边问你在何方。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·兰园醉看梦中人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相约万里流云外，等你归来恋月真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盼远回眸山水笑，兰园醉看梦中人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200912/b463894475d04fbf9c74f9e862895b5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200912/4b48898cfeb54a0e974a528cfce6626b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
